(124, 1257, 4, 2, 'harris-hotel-sentul-city-bogor', '{"en":"Harris Hotel Sentul City Bogor","ind":"Harris Hotel Sentul City Bogor"}', 'Kompleks SICC, Jl. Jendral Sudirman No. 1, Sentul City, Sentul, Bogor, Indonesia', '{"en":"<p>Bogor&rsquo;s famous landmarks include Sentul International Convention center (0.5 km away), Bogor Botanical Garden (5km away), Zoology Museum (6km away), and Bogor Presidential Palace (6km away). Hotel accommodations are carefully selected to meet the guests&rsquo; satisfaction. Staying at Harris Hotel Sentul City would be a good decision. This property offers you a fun accommodation that is suitable for family or business needs, whether for budget traveler, or moneyed travelers.<br /><br />Best Hotel with Great Facilities<br /><br />Staying in Harris Hotel Sentul City will be an enjoyable experience; you can choose among its spacious 160 guestrooms, featuring free high-speed internet connection, air conditioner, IDD telephone, cable TV, in-room safety deposit box, non-smoking, mini bar, hair dryer, and laundry service. It is also equipped with caf&eacute; and restaurants to satisfy your appetite, with wide range selections of dishes from Asian to Western cuisine, and enjoy your favorite cocktail in its bar lounge.<br /><br />Green surrounding, perfect for family stay<br /><br />The venue is ideally located as a part of Sentul International Convention Center with green surrounding and fresh air everywhere. This soothing environment makes a perfect place to stay with your family. Get easy access to Harris Hotel Sentul City. Find yourself in most relaxing gateway during your stay, as it brings the concept of &ldquo;more than a hotel&rdquo;, a complete package for lifestyle, business, and leisure.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p>Landmark Bogor terkenal termasuk pusat Sentul International Convention ( 0,5 km ), Kebun Raya Bogor ( 5 km), Museum Zoologi ( 6 km ), dan Bogor Istana Kepresidenan ( 6 km ). Akomodasi hotel secara hati-hati dipilih untuk me