(215, 1322, 4, 2, 'kosenda-hotel', '{"en":"Kosenda Hotel Jakarta","ind":"Kosenda Hotel Jakarta"}', 'Jl. Wahid Hasyim No 127, Tanah Abang, Thamrin, Jakarta, Indonesia 10240', '{"en":"<p>Many hotels in Thamrin area look like modern, business hotel, but Kosenda Hotel is an exclusive accommodation with unique, funky design and artsy rooms. With striking design elements and beautiful landscape around it, Kosenda Hotel is like a small, unique oasis in the middle of busy Thamrin. The hotel is also close to signature places such as Sarinah Department Store and Jaya Pub.<br /><br />Artistic rooms for memorable stay<br /><br />Kosenda Hotel only has 60 rooms, and each is decorated with simple, contemporary design elements. There are options between twin beds and queen size bed, and there are suites with chic dining area, glass shower box and plush sofa. The bathroom is simple yet beautiful and you get free toiletries. Each room has splashes of bright colors amidst elegant design to give more memorable staying experience, as well as unique lamps and doors.<br /><br />Peaceful Atmosphere and great facilities<br /><br />Kosenda Hotel has beautiful restaurant with various local and international menus, served in exotic, modern-tropical style. Fresh fruit juices and modern take of Indonesian menus are favorites here. Meanwhile, beautiful garden around the hotel creates peaceful atmosphere. Trendy pub with playful design was built near the garden, and there are caf&eacute;, comfortable lobby and shopping area. Services include laundry, concierge, shuttle service and airport transfer. Kosenda Hotel is a unique oasis for travelers among the busy Thamrin area.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p>Banyak hotel di daerah Thamrin terlihat seperti modern, hotel bisnis, tapi Kosenda Hotel adalah akomodasi eksklusif dengan unik, desain funky dan berseni kamar . Dengan mencolok elemen desain dan pemandangan yang indah di sekitarnya, Kosenda Hotel adalah seperti kecil, oasis yang unik di tengah-tengah Thamrin sibuk . Hotel ini juga dekat dengan tempat-tempat tanda tangan seperti Sarinah Department Store dan Jaya Pub .<br /><br />Kamar artistik untuk tinggal kenangan<br /><br />Kosenda Hotel hanya memiliki 60 kamar, dan masing-masing dihiasi dengan sederhana, elemen desain kontemporer . Ada pilihan antara tempat tidur kembar dan Ratu ukuran tempat tidur, dan ada suite dengan apik ruang makan, kaca kotak mandi dan sofa mewah . Kamar mandi sederhana namun indah dan Anda mendapatkan perlengkapan mandi gratis . Setiap kamar memiliki percikan warna-warna cerah di tengah-tengah desain elegan untuk memberikan pengalaman tinggal lebih berkesan, serta lampu dan pintu yang unik .<br /><br />Suasana damai dan fasilitas yang besar<br /><br />Kosenda Hotel memiliki restoran yang indah dengan berbagai menu lokal dan internasional, disajikan dalam eksotis, gaya modern - tropis . Jus buah segar dan modern mengambil menu Indonesia adalah favorit di sini. Sementara itu, taman yang indah di sekitar hotel menciptakan suasana damai . Pub trendi dengan desain playful dibangun dekat taman, dan ada kafe, nyaman lobi dan area perbelanjaan . Layanan meliputi laundry, concierge, layanan antar-jemput dan transfer bandara . Kosenda Hotel adalah sebuah oase yang unik bagi wisatawan di antara daerah Thamrin sibuk .</p>"}', '{"en":"","ind":""}', '', '', '2014/05/02/20140502_115217_3357.jpg', '{"en":"","ind":""}', 4, '', 0, 0, 0, 70, 60, '', '', 0, 'approve', '2014-05-02 11:52:26'),
(216, 1322, 4, 2, 'the-media-hotel-towers', '{"en":"The Media Hotel & Towers","ind":"The Media Hotel & Towers"}', 'Jl. Gunung Sahari Raya, Mangga Dua, Jakarta, Indonesia 10720', '{"en":"<p>Mangga Dua area is a trendy shopping district, and if you love visiting Jakarta to shop, The Media Hotel &amp; Towers is a great accommodation to stay in. This hotel is located near some of the most popular landmarks in Mangga Dua such as ITC Mangga Dua Mall, Jakarta International Expo and Mangga Dua Square.<br /><br />Rooms with modern-minimalist style<br /><br />The Media Hotel &amp; Towers has 350 rooms, and all are designed in modern-minimalist style that is comfortable and welcoming. You can choose the Tower Rooms if you want beautiful city view, Penthouse for exclusive stay, or various suites such as Junior Suite and Presidential Suite for exclusive business or family stay.<br /><br />The Penthouse is a magnificent facility with spacious area, luxurious design with authentic teakwood furniture and chandelier style lamps. The living room has its own garden in the balcony and presents one of the most beautiful accommodations inside the hotel.<br /><br />Facilities and Services<br /><br />There are many great facilities inside The Media Hotel &amp; Towers; there are several themed restaurants and cafes such as The Breeze where you can get breakfast, Sukhothai and Dragon Court for Asian delights, Deli Cake Shop that opens or 24-hour, and poolside bar. Meanwhile, beautiful Acropolis Spa brings Ancient Greece style into modern spa and massage center. The Media Hotel &amp; Towers is a great value luxury hotel in Mangga Dua area with complete facilities and great view.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p>Daerah Mangga Dua adalah distrik perbelanjaan trendi, dan jika Anda suka mengunjungi Jakarta untuk berbelanja, The Media Hotel &amp; Towers adalah akomodasi yang bagus untuk tinggal masuk Hotel ini terletak dekat beberapa landmark yang paling populer di Mangga Dua seperti ITC Mangga Dua Mall, Jakarta International Expo dan Mangga Dua Square.<br /><br />Kamar dengan gaya modern minimalis<br /><br />The Media Hotel &amp; Towers memiliki 350 kamar, dan semua dirancang dengan gaya modern minimalis yang nyaman dan ramah . Anda dapat memilih Menara Rooms jika Anda ingin melihat kota yang indah, Penthouse untuk tinggal eksklusif, atau berbagai suite seperti Junior Suite dan Presidential Suite untuk bisnis eksklusif atau keluarga tinggal .<br /><br />The Penthouse adalah fasilitas megah dengan luas luas, desain mewah dengan furnitur kayu jati asli dan lampu chandelier gaya . Ruang tamu memiliki kebun sendiri di balkon dan menyajikan salah satu akomodasi yang paling indah di dalam hotel .<br /><br />Fasilitas dan Layanan<br /><br />Ada banyak fasilitas yang besar di dalam The Media Hotel &amp; Towers ; ada beberapa restoran dan kafe bertema seperti The Breeze di mana Anda bisa mendapatkan sarapan, Sukhothai dan Dragon Court untuk kelezatan Asia, Deli Cake Shop yang terbuka atau 24 - jam, dan bar tepi kolam . Sementara itu, Acropolis Spa indah membawa Yunani Kuno gaya ke spa dan pijat pusat modern. The Media Hotel &amp; Towers adalah hotel mewah nilai yang besar di daerah Mangga Dua dengan fasilitas lengkap dan pemandangan .</p>"}', '{"en":"","ind":""}', '', '', '2014/05/02/20140502_115421_2697.jpg', '{"en":"","ind":""}', 5, '', 0, 0, 0, 57, 350, '', '', 0, 'approve', '2014-05-02 11:54:25'),
(217, 1322, 4, 2, 'somerset-berlian-jakarta', '{"en":"Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel","ind":"Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel"}', 'Jalan Permata Berlian V. Permata Hijau, Senayan, Jakarta, Indonesia 12210', '{"en":"<p>Permata Hijau is an oasis in the middle of Senayan, and Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel is located there. Hidden between lush garden and greeneries, Somerset Berlian provides modern accommodation with simple yet modern take of a luxurious condominium or apartment. The hotel has strategic location, located near to Senayan Plaza and Golf Course.<br /><br />Apartment-style hotel with great view<br /><br />There are 147 rooms at Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel, and all of them are very modern with simple yet luxurious touch. Each room is decorated so it looks like a fancy apartment, giving familiar and comfortable feeling once you enter the room. The suites have options between 2-bedroom and 3-bedroom, and each has wide living room with modern amenities. Air conditioner, TV, dining room and modern furniture are available in each suite, as long as great view to the entire city.<br /><br />Family-friendly facilities<br /><br />This modern hotel boasts many great facilities such as restaurant, caf&eacute;, swimming pool and shopping area, including swimming pool for kids. For sport, there are tennis court, gym and a golf course that is only 3 km away. Spa, massage and sauna center are guaranteed to make you feel refreshed. Services include laundry, concierge, room service, Wi-Fi, LAN, and meeting room as well as service. Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel is a great apartment-style hotel in Permata Hijau area in Senayan.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p>Permata Hijau adalah sebuah oase di tengah-tengah Senayan, dan Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel terletak di sana. Tersembunyi di antara taman yang rimbun dan tumbuh-tumbuhan, Somerset Berlian menyediakan akomodasi modern dengan mengambil sederhana namun modern dari kondominium mewah atau apartemen . Hotel ini memiliki lokasi strategis, terletak dekat Senayan Plaza dan Lapangan Golf .<br /><br />Hotel bergaya apartemen dengan pemandangan<br /><br />Ada 147 kamar di Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel, dan semua dari mereka sangat modern dengan sentuhan sederhana namun mewah . Setiap kamar dihiasi sehingga terlihat seperti sebuah apartemen mewah, memberikan perasaan akrab dan nyaman setelah Anda memasuki ruangan . Suite memiliki pilihan antara 2 kamar tidur dan 3 kamar tidur, dan masing-masing memiliki ruang tamu yang luas dengan fasilitas modern. AC, TV, ruang makan dan perabotan modern tersedia di setiap suite, asalkan pemandangan ke seluruh kota .<br /><br />Fasilitas keluarga<br /><br />Hotel modern ini menawarkan banyak fasilitas yang besar seperti restoran, kafe, kolam renang dan area perbelanjaan, termasuk kolam renang untuk anak-anak . Untuk olahraga, ada lapangan tenis, pusat kebugaran dan lapangan golf yang hanya 3 km jauhnya . Spa, pijat dan sauna pusat dijamin untuk membuat Anda merasa segar . Layanan meliputi laundry, concierge, layanan kamar, Wi- Fi, LAN, dan ruang pertemuan serta layanan . Somerset Berlian Jakarta Hotel adalah hotel bergaya apartemen besar di daerah Permata Hijau di Senayan .</p>"}', '{"en":"","ind":""}', '', '', '2014/05/02/20140502_115613_3322.jpg', '{"en":"","ind":""}', 5, '', 0, 0, 0, 115, 147, '', '', 0, 'approve', '2014-05-02 11:56:33'),
(218, 1322, 4, 2, 'mulia-hotel', '{"en":"Mulia Hotel Jakarta","ind":"Mulia Hotel Jakarta"}', 'Jl. Asia Afrika Senayan, Senayan, Jakarta, Indonesia 10270', '{"en":"<p>As one of the busiest areas in Jakarta, Senayan has many choices of accommodations, and one of them is Mulia Hotel. This hotel is located in the historical Asia-Afrika Street, near famous landscapes such as Indonesia&rsquo;s House of Representative building, Jakarta Convention Center and Gelora Bung Karno Stadium. This is a great choice for business accommodation in Senayan.<br /><br />Modern rooms with lavish decoration<br /><br />As a luxurious business hotel, Mulia Hotel has really modern yet comfortable rooms and state of the art amenities. All of the hotel&rsquo;s 996 rooms boast lavish decoration with modern amenities such as spacious bathroom, plasma TV, comfy study desk and chair, plush bed, air conditioner and sofa. Each room also boasts great view to the city skyline. Mulia Hotel Jakarta also has Executive Room perfect for luxurious business accommodation and Junior Suite for family travel. The furniture and design only reflect the highest taste.<br /><br />Facilities for leisure and business travel<br /><br />Mulia Hotel has all facilities you need for nice business and leisure travel. There are elegant business center, meeting rooms, executive floor, lounge and ballroom. Wi-Fi is available for free. Meanwhile, for leisure, there are hip bar and night club, shopping area and spa. Restaurant serves modern take of various local dishes, as well as international dishes. Mulia Hotel Jakarta is clearly a representative hotel for business travel in Senayan.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p>Sebagai salah satu daerah tersibuk di Jakarta, Senayan memiliki banyak pilihan akomodasi, dan salah satunya adalah Mulia Hotel . Hotel ini terletak di sejarah Asia - Afrika Street, dekat lanskap terkenal seperti House di Indonesia Perwakilan bangunan, Jakarta Convention Center dan Stadion Gelora Bung Karno . Ini adalah 