(259, 1394, 4, 2, 'hotel-santika-palu', '{"en":"Santika Palu Hotel","ind":"Hotel Santika Palu"}', 'Jalan Moh. Hatta No.18, Palu, Palu, Indonesia 425278', '{"en":"<p>If you go to Palu and need to stay in cheap yet good hotel, you can stay at Hotel Santika Palu. As a new hotel, this is a great accommodation with economic price and complete facilities, and also one of the best in Palu. The hotel has been known as a perfect business and tourist hotel, with modern facilities and friendly service that will make your stay comfortable.<br /><br />Modern and Comfortable Rooms<br />There are 144 rooms in this 3-star hotel, and all are decorated with modern, clean and neat decoration that creates cozy atmosphere. Both Superior and Deluxe bedrooms are spacious, comfortable and have gorgeous views toward the city. All bedrooms are equipped with standard amenities such as large beds (twin or double), bathroom with hot water and shower, TV, air conditioner and standard furniture. 24 hour room service and laundry are available.<br /><br />Complete, Modern Facilities <br />Hotel Santika Palu has exquisite outdoor pool on higher ground with infinity model, giving you excellent view while swimming. Restaurant and caf&eacute; serve various modern dishes, breakfast, beverages, snacks and pastries. Meeting room, business center and Wifi are available for business travelers. You can also use fitness center or order airport transfer for your comfort.<br />Hotel Santika Palu is a great 3-star hotel for business and leisure travelers alike.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p>Jika Anda pergi ke Palu dan harus tinggal di hotel murah namun baik , Anda bisa menginap di Hotel Santika Palu . Sebagai sebuah hotel baru , ini adalah akomodasi yang besar dengan harga ekonomis dan fasilitas yang lengkap , dan juga salah satu yang terbaik di Palu . Hotel ini telah dikenal sebagai bisnis dan wisata hotel yang sempurna , dengan fasilitas modern dan layanan yang ramah yang akan membuat Anda tetap nyaman .<br /><br