(288, 1599, 4, 2, 'le-krasak-boutique-hotel', '{"en":"Le Krasak Boutique Hotel","ind":"Le Krasak Boutique Hotel"}', 'Jl. Krasak No. 9, Tugu Jogja, Yogyakarta, Indonesia ', '{"en":"<p>Tugu area in Yogyakarta has many cheap hotels, but not all provide such homey feeling such as Le Krasak Boutique Hotel. With only 24 bedrooms and artistic interior, this hotel is such an oasis in the middle of city, with rather quite surrounding and complete standard facilities. This is perfect for budget travelers with taste for small, quaint and quiet hotel.<br /><br />Rooms and Amenities<br />24 bedrooms of Le Krasak Boutique Hotel are simple but tastefully furnished, with plush bed, standard furniture and extra seating area in the Suite Room, which is perfect for family holiday. The whole design was made so the hotel has more homey and laidback feeling. The bathroom has hot water and bathtub, and there are free toiletries as well as TV and AC available. Room service and laundry are available for your comfort.<br /><br /></p>","ind":"<p><span id=##002##result_box##002## lang=##002##id##002##><span class=##002##hps##002##>Daerah</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Tugu</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>di</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Yogyakarta</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>memiliki banyak</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>hotel murah,</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>tetapi tidak semua</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>memberikan</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>perasaan nyaman</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>seperti seperti</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Le</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Krasak</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Boutique</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Hotel</span><span>.</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>Dengan hanya</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>24</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>kamar tidur dan</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>interior</span> <span class=##002##hps##002##>artistik</span><